No, but at the moment to me that's his meeting.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:59.000
We met new friend called David through Richard and other friend.

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:07.000
So we've had a bigger group meeting, Skype-ing which is very good fun.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:12.000
So that thing you've got tonight, who are those friends?

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:15.000
Where did you meet them? Obviously before lockdown I presume.

