00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:10.000
I'm awesome. We all have a very good friendship with all of them.

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:16.000
And one of the choir members was my school teacher in Llanwell.

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:20.000
So we're really making great friends now.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:23.000
We miss him a lot.

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:27.000
I think we're missing all, we call it a family I suppose.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:29.000
It's like choir family.

